These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, satire, western
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, car, boat
1. the person watching horror movies is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
4. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | western | satire    |
| Transport     | car    | boat       | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, architect, paramedic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, cricket, baseball
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the paramedic is on the left of the mechanic##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left or far right##3
4. the architect is the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | paramedic | mechanic | architect  |
| Sport   | weightlifting  | cricket  | baseball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, writer, engineer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, folk, soul
1. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
2. the freelancer is on the far right##1
3. the writer is the fan of soul##1
4. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | engineer | writer | freelancer |
| Music-Genre   | ambient        | soul    | folk        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, woodworking, reading
3 different pets are kept: turtle, horse, cat
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
3. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's hobby is reading and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | reading | woodworking | puzzles |
| Pet     | horse  | turtle    | cat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, horror
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | drama | horror |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | bus   | quad-bike   |

