There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, thai
1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the indian##1
2. the thai is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the thai is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
