.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, hot-chocolate
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, tomato, peas
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating cranberry##1
2. the person eating tomato is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate        | lemonade  | iced-tea   |
| Food       | peas | tomato | cranberry |

 #################################

 
