2. the pakistani is the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | cola    | mirinda    | coffee  |
| Nationality   | pakistani | malaysian | egyptian |

