.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, egyptian, british
3 different pets are kept: goat, mouse, ferret
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
2. the british is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the goat##2
4. the owner of the goat is the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | russian | british | egyptian |
| Pet           | mouse    | ferret    | goat       |

