2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
3. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | skydiving    | woodworking   | card-games |
| Sport   | basketball | golf | ice-hockey |

