.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, superhero, horror
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, techno, d&b
1. the fan of techno is in the middle##1
2. the person watching horror movies is between the fan of d&b and the fan of hip-hop##2
3. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of d&b is the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | horror | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | techno  | d&b    |

