.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, thriller
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea    | fanta | coffee         |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | drama  | disaster |

 